     4→//! CanvasChain Symphony – Minting Service
     5→//! --------------------------------------
     6→//! Factory & Strategy pattern–powered NFT minting logic.
     7→//! Creates multilayer NFTs, signs mint payloads with a pluggable crypto
     8→//! backend and broadcasts events onto the internal event-bus.
     9→//!
    10→//! This file purposefully hides transport concerns (gRPC, HTTP, etc.); the
