     2→//! Marketplace ‑ Listing Manager
     3→//!
     4→//! This module is responsible for orchestrating the full life-cycle of NFT
     5→//! listings in the CanvasChain Symphony marketplace micro-service.  
     6→//! It follows Repository + Event Driven patterns to keep storage concerns and
     7→//! side-effects clearly separated from business logic.
     8→//!
     9→//! Responsibilities
    10→//! * Create / update / cancel fixed-price listings
    11→//! * Atomically settle purchases (reserve → transfer → close)
    12→//! * Publish `MarketplaceEvent`s on the internal event bus
    13→//! * Provide a type-safe façade for gRPC handlers & GraphQL resolvers
    14→//!
    15→//! Note: In production, `ListingRepository` would be backed by Postgres or
    16→//! RocksDB; here we ship an in-memory implementation for completeness.
