     2→//! Proposal Engine
     3→//!
     4→//! This module owns the lifecycle of a governance proposal—from
     5→//! creation to finalization—inside the CanvasChain Symphony governance
     6→//! micro-service.  It is intentionally decoupled from concrete storage,
     7→//! crypto or transport layers via small, test-friendly traits so that
     8→//! the engine can be reused inside CLI tools, HTTP controllers or gRPC
     9→//! handlers without recompilation.
    10→
